title: Pool game
text: I really enjoy this pool game. All the rewards and prizes give the game alt of incentive to keep coming back. The only things that bug me are the constant pop up screens that get in the way of the tasks you have at hand like opening a prize box and at the exact comment you tap the screen you hit the pop up.  The other is when you have choose to play a certain table such as Sydney and that game has finished you‚Äôre automatically set up to enter the maximum table for your full coin amount. When this has happened and I have accidentally entered a that table and on the unfortunate side have lost it all, It takes me along time to come back and play the game. I think it has been almost a year now. And I came back to play again and this is still a thing. Other then these two things. I love this game. It is by far the best pool game app I have ever played. No others come close. Thanks for the fun this game has brought me.
